_:Nffc01d2d3a9d45ce9d3b727f9cfdf72e <http://schema.org/description> "Crossrail International (CI) was established by the Department for Transport to help promote UK businesses abroad. It is a specialist advisory practice that works with UK partners to provide strategic advice to clients on the development and delivery of complex rail and metro schemes across the globe. CI is a public corporation of the Department for Transport ." .
